snippet.title: Hum Toh Deewane - Elvish Yadav & Urvashi Rautela | Yasser Desai | Rajat Nagpal | Rana | Anshul Garg
snippet.description:
Anshul Garg presents Hum Toh Deewane featuring Elvish Yadav & Urvashi Rautela. 

Listen on Spotify 👉 https://spotify.link/HuU6Z6Ci4Cb

Audio credits 
Song : Hum toh deewane
Singer Yasser Desai 
Composer Rajat Nagpal

Music Rajat Nagpal

Ingrooves team
Head : Amit Sharma
Team : Nagesh Jadhav, Kajal Israni, Amol Suryavanshi, Lavanya Das, Nishtha sikroria



Lyrics :

Nain tumko  chuney,,
bs baat dil ki suney ,,
Dunia ko bhool kar ,,
Tere hi khaab buney ,,
Tujhme or khuda me koi fark na jaane ,,
Humto deewane deewane deewane ,,
Tere deewane deewane deewane ,

Tujhme or khuda me koi fark na jaane ,,

Hum to deewane deewane ….

Deewane deewane deewane tere hum toh 

Maang lu mai tumhey koi sitaara tuttay ,,
Judkay na phir kabhi rista hamara tutay ,,
Raaton ka ptaa nahi kab savere hue   ,,
Waqt bhi dekhaa na jabse tere hue  ,
Tujhey apna hai kehna ve , 
Mai tere nal rehna ve,,
dekhne k dhundhay bahanay ,,

Humto deewanay ,,deewane ,,

snippet.title: Aquaman and the Lost Kingdom | Trailer
snippet.description:
One king will lead us all. #Aquaman and the Lost Kingdom - Only in theaters December 20.

Director James Wan and Aquaman himself, Jason Momoa—along with Patrick Wilson, Amber Heard, Yahya Abdul-Mateen II and Nicole Kidman—return in the sequel to the highest-grossing DC film of all time: “Aquaman and the Lost Kingdom.”

Having failed to defeat Aquaman the first time, Black Manta, still driven by the need to avenge his father’s death, will stop at nothing to take Aquaman down once and for all. This time Black Manta is more formidable than ever before, wielding the power of the mythic Black Trident, which unleashes an ancient and malevolent force. To defeat him, Aquaman will turn to his imprisoned brother Orm, the former King of Atlantis, to forge an unlikely alliance. Together, they must set aside their differences in order to protect their kingdom and save Aquaman’s family, and the world, from irreversible destruction.

All returning to the roles they originated, Jason Momoa plays Arthur Curry/Aquaman, now balancing his duties as both the King of Atlantis and a new father; Patrick Wilson is Orm, Aquaman’s half-brother and his nemesis, who must now step into a new role as his brother’s reluctant ally; Amber Heard is Mera, Atlantis’ Queen and mother of the heir to the throne; Yahya Abdul-Mateen II is Black Manta, committed more than ever to avenge his father’s death by destroying Aquaman, his family and Atlantis; and Nicole Kidman as Atlanna, a fierce leader and mother with the heart of a warrior. Also reprising their roles are Dolph Lundgren as King Nereus and Randall Park as Dr. Stephen Shin.

Directed by Wan, “Aquaman and the Lost Kingdom” is produced by Peter Safran, Wan and Rob Cowan. The executive producers are Galen Vaisman and Walter Hamada.

The screenplay is by David Leslie Johnson-McGoldrick, from a story by James Wan & David Leslie Johnson-McGoldrick and Jason Momoa & Thomas Pa’a Sibbett, based on characters from DC, Aquaman created by Paul Norris and Mort Weisinger. 

Joining Wan behind-the-camera is his sterling team of “Aquaman” artisans: director of photography Don Burgess (“The Conjuring 2”), production designer Bill Brzeski (“Jumanji: The Next Level”), editor Kirk Morri (“Furious 7”), composer Rupert Gregson-Williams (“Wonder Woman”) and music supervisor is Michelle Silverman (“Malignant”). Visual effects supervisor Nick Davis (“The Clash of the Titans” films, “The Dark Knight”) and costume designer Richard Sale (“Doctor Strange in the Multiverse of Madness,” “Ready Player One”) also join.

Warner Bros. Pictures Presents An Atomic Monster / A Peter Safran Production of A James Wan Film, “Aquaman and the Lost Kingdom,” set to open in theaters internationally beginning 20 December 2023 and in North America on December 20, 2023; it will be distributed worldwide by Warner Bros. Pictures.

Joining Wan behind-the-camera is his sterling team of “Aquaman” artisans: director of photography Don Burgess (“The Conjuring 2”), production designer Bill Brzeski (“Jumanji: The Next Level”), editor Kirk Morri (“Furious 7”), composer Rupert Gregson-Williams (“Wonder Woman”) and music supervisor is Michelle Silverman (“Malignant”). Visual effects supervisor Nick Davis (“The Clash of the Titans” films, “The Dark Knight”) and costume designer Richard Sale (“Doctor Strange in the Multiverse of Madness,” “Ready Player One”) also join.

Warner Bros. Pictures Presents An Atomic Monster / A Peter Safran Production of A James Wan Film, “Aquaman and the Lost Kingdom,” set to open in theaters internationally beginning 20 December 2023 and in North America on December 20, 2023; it will be distributed worldwide by Warner Bros. Pictures.

snippet.title: Introducing iPhone 15 Pro | Apple
snippet.description:
The new iPhone 15 Pro and iPhone 15 Pro Max are ready for action. Built with aerospace-grade titanium for our lightest, most powerful Pro models ever.

The new Pro camera system pushes the limits of what’s possible on a smartphone, giving photographers the equivalent of seven pro lenses ranging from 13 mm on the Ultra Wide camera to 120 mm on the 5x Telephoto camera on iPhone 15 Pro Max.

Filmmakers can now record video in ProRes 4K at 60 fps directly to an external drive. The addition of a USB-C connector brings superfast USB 3 transfer speeds, along with support for pro formats that massively improve the workflow between shooting and post-production.

The new design also includes a customizable Action button for quicker access to your favorite feature.*

And the A17 Pro chip with a 6-core GPU introduces a whole new level of immersive mobile gaming performance. 

In short, the new titanium iPhone 15 Pro is our most powerful photo-taking, movie-making, game-playing iPhone ever.

Learn more about iPhone 15 Pro and iPhone 15 Pro Max: https://apple.co/3PBuiJq

Audio Descriptions: https://apple.co/44QCI3W

snippet.description:

Daya wakes up at a lady's house and does not remember his own name. The lady calls Team CID to pick him up. ACP Pradyuman and Abhijeet arrive with the team but Daya refuses to recognize any of them. Abhijeet tries to make him remember how he had gone to investigate about a case. How did Daya end up like this? Stay tuned to find out!

Show Name: CID

• Shivaji Satam as ACP Pradyuman

• Ashutosh Gowariker as Sr. Inspector Virendra

• Aditya Srivastava as Sr. Inspector Abhijeet
• Shraddha Musale as Dr. Tarika
• Ansha Sayed as Sub-Inspector Purvi
Episode: 1377

#CID #सीआईडी #CID2023 #CrimeThrillers #CrimeMysteries #Mysteries #Horror #LIVCrime #NewCID #Crime #NewCID #latestcid 

About CID:
-----------------
The first thrilling investigative series on Indian Television is today one of the most popular shows on Sony Entertainment Television. Dramatic and absolutely unpredictable, C.I.D. has captivated viewers over the last eleven years and continues to keep audiences glued to their television sets with its thrilling plots and excitement. Also interwoven in its fast-paced plots are the personal challenges that the C.I.D. team faces with non-stop adventure, tremendous pressure, and risk, all in the name of duty. The series consists of hard-core police procedural stories dealing with investigation, detection, and suspense. The protagonists of the serial are an elite group of police officers belonging to the Crime Investigation Department of the police force, led by ACP Pradyuman [played by the dynamic Shivaji Satam]. While the stories are plausible, there is an emphasis on dramatic plotting and technical complexities faced by the police. At every stage, the plot throws up intriguing twists and turns to keep the officers on the move as they track criminals, led by the smallest of clues.

snippet.title: Jaya Kishori - Parenting tips & spiritual growth बच्चों के लिए आध्यात्म | Bharti Harsh LOL PODCAST 1
snippet.description:
Bharti TV के LOL Podcast के पहले एपिसोड में, भारती और हर्ष ने जया किशोरी जी को अपने गेस्ट के तौर पर आमंत्रित किया। उन्होंने चर्चा की कि बच्चों के जीवन में आध्यात्मिकता कैसे पेश किया जा सकता है। उन्होंने माता-पिता के लिए मूलभूत सुझाव और अपने व्यक्तिगत अनुभवों का सांझा किया। इसका उद्देश्य बच्चों के पालन-पोषण में आध्यात्मिक मूल्यों और प्रैक्टिकल सुझावों की समझ प्रदान करना है। यह एपिसोड वे लोगों के लिए बेहद महत्वपूर्ण है जो अपने बच्चों को आध्यात्मिक दृष्टिकोण से पालना चाहते हैं। भारती, हर्ष , और जया किशोरी के साथ जुड़ें और उनके साथ जुड़कर देखें कि आने वाली पीढ़ियों के पालने में आध्यात्मिकता का महत्व क्या है।

In the debut of LOL Podcast on Bharti TV, Bharti and Haarsh invite Jaya Kishori to discuss introducing spirituality to kids. They share insights and tips for parents and caregivers. Perfect for anyone interested in raising spiritually aware children. 

(00:00) - Start of the episode   
(02:02) - Bachchon ke jeevan me spirituality  ko kaise introduce karein ?
(06:17)-  Bhagwan ka bachpan 
(09:01) -Bharti ki shararate 
(10:14)- Female spiritual leaders itni kam Kyu hai...?
(14:36)- Shaadi
(22:55)- Jaya Kishori & food 
(28:23)- Boogie Woogie
(30:13)- kisi ladke ne kabhi propose kiya hai ?
(33:54) pariwaar ko ek saath khaana, khana chahiye 
(34:47)-  spirituality & success.
(43:05)-Shrimad Bhagavad story .
(45:01)- Meaning of bhagwat Puran 
(50:50)-How to be relatable among youth?
(54:07)-Jaya Kishori listens to Rajeshwaranand Ji Maharaj
(59:01)-End Note 

#jayakishori #podcast #bhartisingh #harshlimbachiya

A shocking incident happens wherein the Team of CID officers are all set to start their investigation for a new case and they end up looking at a strange site, that a man was lying down unconscious on the floor inside a mall. Now, Stay Tuned to know who was this man and what had happened to him.

Show Name: CID 
Show Cast & Characters: 
• Shivaji Satam as ACP Pradyuman

#CID #सीआईडी #CID2023 #CrimeThrillers #CrimeMysteries #Mysteries #CIDSeries #LIVCrime #NewCID #LatestCID #Crime #taleofcouples

About CID:
-----------------
The first thrilling investigative series on Indian Television is today one of the most popular shows on Sony Entertainment Television. Dramatic and absolutely unpredictable, C.I.D. has captivated viewers over the last eleven years and continues to keep audiences glued to their television sets with its thrilling plots and excitement. Also interwoven in its fast-paced plots are the personal challenges that the C.I.D. team faces with non-stop adventure, tremendous pressure, and risk, all in the name of duty. The series consists of police procedural stories dealing with investigation, detection, and suspense. The protagonists of the serial are an elite group of police officers belonging to the Crime Investigation Department of the police force, led by ACP Pradyuman [played by the dynamic Shivaji Satam]. While the stories are plausible, there is an emphasis on dramatic plotting and technical complexities faced by the police. At every stage, the plot throws up intriguing twists and turns to keep the officers on the move as they track criminals, led by the smallest of clues.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 3875 | 13 Sep 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3875: Sabne Chintan Ko Chuna
--------------------------------------------------------
Everyone at the Gokuldham society is touched by the story of Chintan and his parents and plans to help them. To shatter the Iccha Purti matki, everyone chooses Chintan as an act of assisting and helping him. He is assisted in breaking the matki by Tapu Sena, but he keeps falling. Tapu intervenes and helps Chintan to reach the top and break the handi. Chintan successfully breaks the handi in his third attempt and everyone dances to the beats of dhol celebrating the auspicious occasion of Dahi handi. Watch the episode to know more.


Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3875, 13 Sep 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

नमस्ते दोस्तों!
The Ranveer Show हिंदी के 196th Episode में आप सभी का स्वागत है. आज के Podcast में हमारे साथ जुड़ चुके हैं मशहूर कवि Kumar Vishwas, जिनकी कविताओं को लोगों से ढ़ेर सारा प्यार मिलता है। साथ ही ये हिंदी के Professor भी रह चुके हैं। अपने जीवन के कुछ साल इन्होंने राजनीति में भी बिताए हैं। 

इस Podcast में हम बात करेंगे ढ़ेर सारी बातें Kumar Vishwas की Life Story, Political Journey, Political Ideology, Anna Hazare, PM Modi, 2024 Elections और Social Media के बारे में।

साथ-ही-साथ हम बात करेंगे शिव तांडव का रहस्य, Spirituality और Religion, Politicians, GenZ की Problems और Creative Transformation के बारे में और भी ढ़ेर सारी बातें। 

मैं आशा करता हूँ कि ये Video आप सभी Viewers को पसंद आएगा। खास तौर पर उन सभी को जिन्हें Kumar Vishwas की Life के बारे में जानने में Interest है। 

Future Of India, Who Will Be India's Next PM और Young Leaders In Politics जैसी चीज़ों के बारे में हम Discuss करेंगे इस Hindi Podcast में सिर्फ और सिर्फ आपके Favourite BeerBiceps Hindi Channel Ranveer Allahbadia पर।

snippet.description:
#g20summit  #saudiarabia #anuragtalks
Check out more details about ICICI NFO 👇
http://bit.ly/3LlTdOx
 
The G20 or Group of 20 is an intergovernmental forum comprising 19 sovereign countries, the European Union (EU), and the African Union (AU). It works to address major issues related to the global economy, such as international financial stability, climate change mitigation and sustainable development.

On the sidelines of the G20 Summit in New Delhi, a Memorandum of Understanding (MoU) was signed between the Governments of India, the US, Saudi Arabia, the European Union, the UAE, France, Germany and Italy to establish the India – Middle East – Europe Economic Corridor (IMEC).
The IMEC is being envisioned as a network of transport corridors, including railway lines and sea lanes, that is expected to aid economic growth through integration between Asia, the Arabian Gulf, and Europe.

snippet.title: Filmymoji || Middle Class Madhu || Vakrathunda Episode 01  || MCM
snippet.description:
Filmymoji Middle Class Madhu Vakrathunda Episode 01  MCM

Filmymoji releases its much awaited webseries for the year, Vakrathundaya, one of the many names of Lord Ganesha on the eve of his Vinayaka Chavithi festive season. This year, Mooshika decides to come down onto Earth to teach Middle class Madhu a very valuable lesson. Like always Middle class Madhu along with Mahesh, Balli and Budatha decides to collect donations for Ganesh Chathurdhi festival so as to get the idol and do the Pooja till nimarjanam time. Watch the full episode to find out the magic Mooshika brings into Madhu’s life.

snippet.title: Daya ने Cook किया Jetha के लिए Special Dinner | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | 11 Sep 2023
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to Sony Pal: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCw7xjxzbMwgBSmbeYwqYRMg

As Jethalal had already reached his office, so Daya in between his work rings him up and tells him that she would be preparing something tasty for dinner, listening to this line Jetha gets extremely excited and refuses to eat anything from outside, so that he can save his hunger for the delicious dinner treat. Now, Stay Tuned to know what special will Daya prepare for Jetha and will that excite him or it will taste like the normal regular food.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episode No - 697
Produced By -  Asit Kumarr Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sonypal #Latest #tmkoc #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo 


About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi), an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or be prepared to leave the premises.

snippet.title: Ehraam-e-Junoon Episode 40 Teaser - 12th September 2023 - HAR PAL GEO
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Ehraam-e-Junoon Episode 40 Teaser - 12th September 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

"Ehraam-e-Junoon" follows the story of a young and immensely beautiful girl named Shanzay, who is filled with pride and stubbornness due to her upper-class upbringing. Shanzay believes that money can buy everything, including happiness. 

Despite her high standards, Shanzay is yet to find a man who can impress her until she meets Shayan at an event. Shayan is a handsome young man from a middle-class family, who takes up a job as a pizza delivery boy to make ends meet. Shanzay who is immediately drawn to Shayan wants to provide him with a better lifestyle however, Shayan keeps his distance and refuses to accept any of Shanzay’s advances.

As the story unfolds, Shanzay and Shayan's paths cross again and again, and Shanzay begins to question her beliefs about love and money. Will Shayan be the one to break through Shanzay's walls of pride and stubbornness, or will she continue to chase after superficial things?

The drama serial "Ehraam-e-Junoon" promises to take viewers on a rollercoaster ride of emotions as it explores the themes of love, pride, and class differences.

Writer: Jahanzeb Qamar
Director: Syed Ramish Rizvi
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :

Nimra Khan as Sajeela

snippet.title: Uppum Mulakum 2 | Flowers | EP# 337
snippet.description:
പാറുക്കുട്ടിയുടെ ഉറ്റചങ്ങാതി ആമി എത്തിയിരിക്കുകയാണ്. വീട്ടിലെ പ്രശ്നങ്ങളൊക്കെ ഇരുവരും പങ്കുവയ്ക്കുകയാണ്. ക്ലാസ് കഴിഞ്ഞ് വമ്പൻ സർപ്രൈസുമായി പാറുക്കുട്ടിയുടെ ഉറ്റ ചങ്ങാതി ആമി എത്തുമെന്ന് വാക്ക് നൽകിയിരിക്കുകയാണ്. എന്തായിരിക്കും ആ സർപ്രൈസ്? 

Parukutty's best friend Amy has arrived. Both of them are sharing all the problems at home. Parukutty's best friend Amy has promised to come after class with a big surprise. What will that surprise be?

Ehraam-e-Junoon Episode 39 - [Eng Sub] - Neelam Muneer - Imran Abbas - Digitally Presented by Sandal Beauty Cream - 12th September 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Ehraam-e-Junoon Digitally Presented by Sandal Beauty Cream

"Ehraam-e-Junoon" follows the story of a young and immensely beautiful girl named Shanzay, who is filled with pride and stubbornness due to her upper-class upbringing. Shanzay believes that money can buy everything, including happiness. 

Despite her high standards, Shanzay is yet to find a man who can impress her until she meets Shayan at an event. Shayan is a handsome young man from a middle-class family, who takes up a job as a pizza delivery boy to make ends meet. Shanzay who is immediately drawn to Shayan wants to provide him with a better lifestyle however, Shayan keeps his distance and refuses to accept any of Shanzay’s advances.

As the story unfolds, Shanzay and Shayan's paths cross again and again, and Shanzay begins to question her beliefs about love and money. Will Shayan be the one to break through Shanzay's walls of pride and stubbornness, or will she continue to chase after superficial things?

The drama serial "Ehraam-e-Junoon" promises to take viewers on a rollercoaster ride of emotions as it explores the themes of love, pride, and class differences.

Ehraam-e-Junoon Digitally Presented by Sandal Beauty Cream

"Ehraam-e-Junoon" follows the story of a young and immensely beautiful girl named Shanzay, who is filled with pride and stubbornness due to her upper-class upbringing. Shanzay believes that money can buy everything, including happiness. 

Despite her high standards, Shanzay is yet to find a man who can impress her until she meets Shayan at an event. Shayan is a handsome young man from a middle-class family, who takes up a job as a pizza delivery boy to make ends meet. Shanzay who is immediately drawn to Shayan wants to provide him with a better lifestyle however, Shayan keeps his distance and refuses to accept any of Shanzay’s advances.

As the story unfolds, Shanzay and Shayan's paths cross again and again, and Shanzay begins to question her beliefs about love and money. Will Shayan be the one to break through Shanzay's walls of pride and stubbornness, or will she continue to chase after superficial things?

The drama serial "Ehraam-e-Junoon" promises to take viewers on a rollercoaster ride of emotions as it explores the themes of love, pride, and class differences.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 3874 | 12 Sep 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3874: Ek Pareshaan Parivar
--------------------------------------------------------
Bagha and Bawri are enthusiastic about the Matki activity at Gokuldham Society, so they dress up and make their way to the ram. Bhide reiterates the regulations for the Matki competition to avoid misunderstanding. Bhide invites Champaklal to reveal the name of the person who would have the golden opportunity to shatter the "Iccha Purti matki" according to Janmashtami tradition. A couple and their son arrive at Gokuldham Society to witness the program as Champaklal takes up a letter from the glass jar. The pair further informs Gokuldham villagers that their kid suffers from an illness that physicians are unable to diagnose and that he is fighting for his life. How would the Gokuldhams assist this couple?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3874, 12 Sep 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Director James Wan and Aquaman himself, Jason Momoa—along with Patrick Wilson, Amber Heard, Yahya Abdul-Mateen II and Nicole Kidman—return in the sequel to the highest-grossing DC film of all time: “Aquaman and the Lost Kingdom.”

Having failed to defeat Aquaman the first time, Black Manta, still driven by the need to avenge his father’s death, will stop at nothing to take Aquaman down once and for all. This time Black Manta is more formidable than ever before, wielding the power of the mythic Black Trident, which unleashes an ancient and malevolent force. To defeat him, Aquaman will turn to his imprisoned brother Orm, the former King of Atlantis, to forge an unlikely alliance. Together, they must set aside their differences in order to protect their kingdom and save Aquaman’s family, and the world, from irreversible destruction.

All returning to the roles they originated, Jason Momoa plays Arthur Curry/Aquaman, now balancing his duties as both the King of Atlantis and a new father; Patrick Wilson is Orm, Aquaman’s half-brother and his nemesis, who must now step into a new role as his brother’s reluctant ally; Amber Heard is Mera, Atlantis’ Queen and mother of the heir to the throne; Yahya Abdul-Mateen II is Black Manta, committed more than ever to avenge his father’s death by destroying Aquaman, his family and Atlantis; and Nicole Kidman as Atlanna, a fierce leader and mother with the heart of a warrior. Also reprising their roles are Dolph Lundgren as King Nereus and Randall Park as Dr. Stephen Shin.

Directed by Wan, “Aquaman and the Lost Kingdom” is produced by Peter Safran, Wan and Rob Cowan. The executive producers are Galen Vaisman and Walter Hamada.

The screenplay is by David Leslie Johnson-McGoldrick, from a story by James Wan & David Leslie Johnson-McGoldrick and Jason Momoa & Thomas Pa’a Sibbett, based on characters from DC, Aquaman created by Paul Norris and Mort Weisinger. 

Joining Wan behind-the-camera is his sterling team of “Aquaman” artisans: director of photography Don Burgess (“The Conjuring 2”), production designer Bill Brzeski (“Jumanji: The Next Level”), editor Kirk Morri (“Furious 7”), composer Rupert Gregson-Williams (“Wonder Woman”) and music supervisor is Michelle Silverman (“Malignant”). Visual effects supervisor Nick Davis (“The Clash of the Titans” films, “The Dark Knight”) and costume designer Richard Sale (“Doctor Strange in the Multiverse of Madness,” “Ready Player One”) also join.

Warner Bros. Pictures Presents An Atomic Monster / A Peter Safran Production of A James Wan Film, “Aquaman and the Lost Kingdom,” set to open in theaters internationally beginning 20 December 2023 and in North America on December 20, 2023; it will be distributed worldwide by Warner Bros. Pictures.

snippet.description:
Sagar Alias Jacky Reloaded is a 2009 Indian film directed by Amal Neerad. It is a  sequel to the 1987 film Irupatham Noottandu and Mohanlal reprise his role as Sagar Alias Jacky. The film was written by S. N. Swamy and produced by Antony Perumbavoor under the company Aashirvad Cinemas. It also features Shobana, Bhavana, Manoj K. Jayan, Suman, and Sampath Raj in supporting roles.
Sagar Alias Jacky Reloaded released on 26 March 2009. The film won the Kerala State Film Award for Best Choreography for Dinesh Kumar.

Directed By : Amal Neerad
Written By : S. N. Swamy

snippet.title: Dastak Mayray Dil Pay | Episode 133 | Turkish Drama | SenCal Kapimi | 14 September 2023
snippet.description:
Dastak Mayray Dil Pay Episode 133 also called Sencal Kapimi or You Knock on my Door is a Turkish Drama in Urdu Dubbing dated 14 September 2023

🎉 Subscribe @Urdu1Officialchannel  Youtube Channel and don't forget to click the Bell icon  , you'll be the first to know about our new uploads, behind-the-scenes content . Join us on this journey, and let's create amazing memories together!

#urdu1 #sencalkapimi #dastakmayraydilpay 

Eda is a bright, beautiful young woman working part time with her florist Aunt. She dreams of getting her degree and moving to Italy, but her dreams are shattered when the heir to the Bolat Holding Company cancels her scholarship. 

Now only two things keep her going - her love of flowers and her hatred for Serkan Bolat. When Serkan comes to speak at Eda’s university, Eda protests strongly. A series of events then leaves these two handcuffed together for most of the day when Eda learns that Serkan really is everything she hates: arrogant, self-centred and a complete control freak. 

When the media mistakenly links the two, Serkan plans to use Eda to get his ex-girlfriend back who had left him and got engaged to another man. The unlikely pair come to an agreement. Eda will pretend to be Serkan’s fiancée, and he will restore her scholarship in return. The arrangement will only last for a couple of months until his ex’s wedding but pretending to be the fiancée of Istanbul’s most eligible bachelor turns out to be a lot harder than Eda has imagined.

A couple had come to a dark and a dingy place to spend time with each other. When they were chatting with each other she felt that something was inside the well besides them. When they checked it they found something very unexpected inside it. They immediately called Team CID. Keep watching to unravel the story ahead.

Show Name: CID

• Shivaji Satam as ACP Pradyuman
• Dinesh Phadnis as Inspector Fredricks aka Freddy

#CID #सीआईडी #CID2023 #CrimeThrillers #CrimeMysteries #Mysteries #Horror #LIVCrime #Crime #NewCID #LatestCID #kidnapseries

About CID:
-----------------
Dramatic and absolutely unpredictable, C.I.D. has captivated viewers over the last eleven years and continues to keep audiences glued to their television sets with its thrilling plots and excitement. Also interwoven in its fast-paced plots are the personal challenges that the C.I.D. team faces non-stop adventure, tremendous pressure, and risk, all in the name of duty. The series consists of hard-core police procedural stories dealing with investigation, detection, and suspense. The protagonists of the serial are an elite group of police officers belonging to the Crime Investigation Department of the police force, led by ACP Pradyuman [played by the dynamic Shivaji Satam. While the stories are plausible, there is an emphasis on dramatic plotting and technical complexities faced by the police. At every stage, the plot throws up intriguing twists and turns to keep the officers on the move as they track criminals, led by the smallest of clues.

Ehraam-e-Junoon Digitally Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream

"Ehraam-e-Junoon" follows the story of a young and immensely beautiful girl named Shanzay, who is filled with pride and stubbornness due to her upper-class upbringing. Shanzay believes that money can buy everything, including happiness. 

Despite her high standards, Shanzay is yet to find a man who can impress her until she meets Shayan at an event. Shayan is a handsome young man from a middle-class family, who takes up a job as a pizza delivery boy to make ends meet. Shanzay who is immediately drawn to Shayan wants to provide him with a better lifestyle however, Shayan keeps his distance and refuses to accept any of Shanzay’s advances.

As the story unfolds, Shanzay and Shayan's paths cross again and again, and Shanzay begins to question her beliefs about love and money. Will Shayan be the one to break through Shanzay's walls of pride and stubbornness, or will she continue to chase after superficial things?

The drama serial "Ehraam-e-Junoon" promises to take viewers on a rollercoaster ride of emotions as it explores the themes of love, pride, and class differences.

snippet.title: Gunwanti ने Yuvraj के दिल में Ichha के खिलाफ भर दिया है ज़हर! | Uttaran | Full Episode | Ep. 844
snippet.description:
Ichha Stumbles Upon Her Son, Yuvraj Who Seems Like A Spoilt Brat. But They Both Can't Recognize Each Other. Yuvraj Comes Back Home And Where Gunwanti Has Filled His Heart With Hatred For Ichha.

Gunwanti ने Yuvraj के दिल में Ichha के खिलाफ भर दिया है ज़हर! | Uttaran | उतरन | Full Episode | Ep. 844


--------
📺 Welcome to the captivating world of 'Uttaran' on Colors TV! 🎬

🤝 Join us on this roller-coaster journey of friendship, love, and betrayal as we delve into the lives of two extraordinary friends from starkly contrasting backgrounds.

👸 Meet Tapasya, the pampered and privileged daughter of a wealthy man, and her best friend, Ichcha, who comes from a humble background as the daughter of a maid. Despite society's barriers, their unbreakable bond challenges conventions and stands the test of time.

💔 Love takes center stage when Veer, whose marriage proposal was rejected by Tapasya, finds solace in the companionship of Ichcha. But what ensues is a whirlwind of emotions as jealousy and heartbreak threaten to tear apart the inseparable duo.

💍 Witness a gripping twist when Tapasya, fueled by spite, takes a drastic step and marries Veer, setting off a chain of events that creates a complex love triangle. Veer finds himself torn between the two friends, entangled in a web of emotions.

🔄 Spanning over thousands of episodes, 'Uttaran' takes you on an emotional roller-coaster, exploring the lives of these characters, their triumphs, their struggles, and the undeniable fate that intertwines their destinies.

👨‍👩‍👧‍👦 As the story unfolds, follow the lives of their children and witness how the choices made by their parents continue to shape their future, testing their bonds and unraveling new mysteries.

🔥 Brace yourself for a gripping tale of love, loyalty, and sacrifice that will keep you on the edge of your seats, episode after episode.

🔔 Subscribe to our channel and hit the notification bell to stay updated on the episodes of 'Uttaran' and join the discussions with fans from all around the world.

📣 Share this description with your friends and family who love engaging drama and unforgettable storytelling. Let's embark on this unforgettable journey together with 'Uttaran'! 🌟

snippet.title: Introducing iPhone 15 | WOW | Apple
snippet.description:
Now with Dynamic Island. A new 48MP Main camera. 2x Telephoto. Next-generation portraits. USB-C. All-day battery life. Aluminum design. Durable color-infused glass. Ceramic Shield. Water resistance. Five new colors. iPhone 15 is here. And totally jam-packed. WOW.
